{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"124b01c8aa","title":"关于党员和团员的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"995b191a13","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"124b01c8aa"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"56d7b2e72b","name":"王朝琪"},{"id":"65f3332453","name":"阎乃犹"},{"id":"7991a1af47","name":"郭士英"},{"id":"8d74014dce","name":"云立峰"},{"id":"ae8f348f9b","name":"禹瀚"},{"id":"bae125b924","name":"陶仲侃"},{"id":"ea25ac8f66","name":"西北农学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3204dcdcb5","type":"title","text":"关于党员和团员的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"124b01c8aa"},{"id":"9cd5b58475","type":"authors","text":"西北农学院王朝琪阎乃犹云立峰郭士英禹瀚陶仲侃","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"124b01c8aa"},{"id":"3cd7cb2bdf","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“有些人一入党就不认群众了，所谓旧社会一入龙门，六亲不认。”(外语教研组讲师　王朝琪)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"124b01c8aa"},{"id":"b57c7a99f3","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“群众看某单位同志傲慢起来了，便说他可能入党了。”“老党员比新党员好，但有些老党员变的不如以前了。”(园艺系副教授  阎乃犹)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"124b01c8aa"},{"id":"da0fdd94b7","type":"paragraph","text":"3．“党现在国民党气氛愈来越严重。”(林学系讲师　云立峰)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"124b01c8aa"},{"id":"4785eb5de0","type":"paragraph","text":"4．“现时的共产党员，就没有一个使我学习的。”(植保系讲师　郭士英)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"124b01c8aa"},{"id":"27e571042c","type":"paragraph","text":"5．“我们学校党委和党员是第一主人，团员是第二主人，非党团学生是第三主人，非党团教师和职工是靠劳力吃饭的，教师成了希腊时代的‘教仆’。”(农学系教授　禹瀚)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"124b01c8aa"},{"id":"cb378c07f6","type":"paragraph","text":"6．“共产主义无产阶级，我看我们学校，有很多阶级，党团员有、教授有、助教还有、工人也有，好象这个学校有贵族阶级存在。”我校“以党的威信欺骗群众”。(化学系教授　陶仲侃)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"124b01c8aa"},{"id":"94c18322ba","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《西北农学院右派言论及错误言论汇集》(西北农学院马列主义教研组编印，1957年12月)。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"124b01c8aa"}],"page":{"id":"037440dcd1","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"124b01c8aa","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}